ygData.messageBody:
Yup, I got the itch and I logged back on last
night. It was cool to see my guild buddies again and I
hope to spend some quality playing time. Does anyone
have any equip I can use? My lvl 30 wiz only has a
stein of moggok, a crude stein and a dragoon dirk!!
THAT'S IT!! I know Smoothie will help out but I could
use all the help I can get! My guild buddies gave me
a green silken drape and a +3int earring, that
should get me started, see yas online!!!!<br><br>Jonquil
Fizzalot<br>Lvl 30 Wizard<br>Mystic Companions
